What's Not in v1

  These APIs exist but I'd skip them in the first build to stay lean:

  - Analytics (/analytics/summary, /trends, /categories, /members) — useful
  later for a "Stats" tab
  - Tags — add to expenses in v2 once core loop is stable
  - Recurring expenses — useful for rent but complex UX, v2
  - Activity feed as its own screen — show on Home, skip dedicated tab for now
  - Custom categories — use system categories, add custom in v2

